-- MOVES-Marnix van den Berge joins Capital Group from CBP Quilvest
-- 
-- Tue Sep 02, 2014 07:12AM EDT
-- None



Sept 2 (Reuters) - Investment manager Capital Group said it appointed Marnix van den Berge business development manager for the Benelux region, as it looks to build presence in key European markets.

Van den Berge, who has 15 years of experience, joins from wealth management firm CBP Quilvest, where he was the head of investor solutions, Capital Group said in a statement.